outfit_data.top: A cream silk blouse with a dramatic puffed sleeve and plunging neckline, featuring intricate embroidered detailing in taupe thread.
outfit_data.bottom: Wide-leg khaki velvet trousers with an exaggerated high waistline, cascading down to the floor in a voluminous drape.
outfit_data.shoes: Black leather knee-high boots with a pointed toe and a chunky heel, accented by silver buckles.
outfit_data.extras: A camel cashmere oversized coat draped loosely over the shoulders, fastening at the front with an antique gold clasp. Large statement earrings made of mushroom-colored satin and aged brass complete the look.
